it describes gilmore's FOIA request for (!) the entire escrow
database. <p>

-meng <p>

&gt;From mengwong@pobox.upenn.edu  Tue Mar 15 01:13:06 1994
Posted-Date: Mon, 14 Mar 94 20:26:58 PST
