<P>
<LI> Other (unassigned)
     <UL>
     <LI> Andrew Hooper, ahooper@eniac.seas.upenn.edu (absent)
     <LI> Jeff Chung, jdchung@seas (late)
     <LI> Dhaneesh kumbhani@seas (absent)
     <LI> Dave millar@pobox (absent)
     <LI> Sarah pong@seas (floated off)
     <LI> Carter Page, cpage@seas (floated off)
     </UL>
</MENU>

