<BODY>

<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=6>Migration Dialogue</FONT></B></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=2>Philip Martin and Michael Teitelbaum</FONT></B></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=2>Co-Directors</FONT></B></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=2>1004 Eagle Place</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=2>Davis, California 95616</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=2>(916) 752-1530 (Tel)</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=2>(916) 758-4928 (Fax)</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=2>(916) 752-5614(Fax)<BR>
<BR>
</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=4>Immigration and Integration Issues in
the 1990s:</FONT></B></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=4>Focus on Europe <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
</FONT></B></CENTER>
<P>
