<P>
<B><FONT SIZE=2>9 am </FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2>Reducing Immigration
Pressures </FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Moderator: Philip Martin </FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Speakers: Michael Teitelbaum, Sloan Foundation, and
Vice Chair, U.S. Commission on Immigration Reform and Elmar H&ouml;nekopp,
Economist, German Institute for Labor Market Research <BR>
